Hewlett-Packard Names Mayer Senior Vice President of Networking

-- B y   L i s a   R a p a p o r t
-- 
2011-10-04T12:20:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/hewlett-packard-names-mayer-senior-vice-president-of-networking.html
Hewlett-Packard Co. (HPQ)  named Bethany
Mayer senior vice president of the networking business unit,
reporting to  Dave Donatelli , executive vice president of
enterprise servers, storage, networking and technology services,
the  Palo Alto , California-based company said today in a
statement.  Previously, Mayer was vice president of marketing for
enterprise servers, storage and networking.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lisa Rapaport in New York at 
 lrapaport1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Lisa Rapaport at 
 lrapaport1@bloomberg.net  